portant. I really enjoyed reading Bill Gates’ testimony earlier talk-
ing  about  the  two  million  new  jobs  that  will  be  created  in  the  fu-
ture. It is our job to make sure the students of today are ready for
those  two  million  jobs  that  are  coming  in  the  future.  STEM  in  our
Texarkana  community  is  really  doing  well.  We  actually  started  off
at  the  high  school  level  a  few  years  ago.  In  fact,  the  Dean  of  the
