to  Morriss  Elementary  last  August.  That  started  last  August,
which  you’re  seeing  today.  Then  starting  off  this  fall  we  will  be
starting  with  our  sixth  grade  at  a  part  of  the  academy  of  Texas
Middle School, so it has STEM in Texas I.S.D. as well.

