jects where they won’t be math and science nerds? Is there any bet-
ter way to ask it?

Mr.  RUSSELL.  No.  That  is  an  excellent  way.  In  fact,  Ms.  Morriss
asked  that  question  before  she  would  allow  us  to  put  her  name  on
