she has quite a passion in the fine arts and again would not allow
her  name  on  a  building  that  did  not  take  great  strides  to  do  that.
If  you  will  look  at  the  stage  that  you’re  sitting  on  right  now  and
all  the  lights  and  the  sound  equipment,  if  I  could  talk  all  of  you
into  coming  back  to  the  next  program  of  the  students  here  in  the
