tween  academies  and  still  be  okay.  So,  while  we  are  concentrating
more  and  have  much  more  of  a  flare,  it’s  not  at  age  five  you’re  all
of  a  sudden  deciding  what  you  want  to  be  at  23  and  you’re  locked
in and hurt and not well rounded otherwise.

